snippet.title: Planet Coaster 2 | Pre Order Trailer
snippet.description:
Get ready to create a splash on November 6th when Planet Coaster 2 comes to PC and console 🌊 Pre-order now and get extra bonus content*: https://fron.dev/YT-PC2-PreorderNow

*The 'Bonus Ride Collection' includes an 'Outamax' water coaster, 'The Cube' thrill ride and an 'FD Vision' rotating ride.  

Create a coaster and water park paradise in Planet Coaster 2: build and customise thrilling roller coasters and incredible water slides, manage the ultimate theme park experience, and share your thrilling creations.  

🎢 Design epic coasters and rides!  
🌊 All new water attractions –  welcome pools, flumes and more!  
🎡 New tools for expanded management 
🌲 New themes and scenery – customise everything! 
🤝Build parks with other players – one park manager at a time 

#PlanetCoaster2 #CreateASplash #FrontierDevelopments #Xbox #PlayStation #PCGaming #Games #Gaming #GameTrailers 

For more news and information about Planet Coaster 2:  

Website:  https://www.planetcoaster.com/  
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@officialplanetgames 
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/planetcoaster/ 
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/PlanetCoaster/ 
X: https://x.com/planetcoaster
Discord: https://discord.gg/smDaNheEwv
